  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Mechanoids are a very strange race &#8211; they =
exist
  as pure logic, living inside computer networks. They have no physical for=
m,
  but they can project their presence on holographic displays or video scre=
ens.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=3D"Picture_x0020_0" o=
:spid=3D"_x0000_s1026"
   type=3D"#_x0000_t75" style=3D'position:absolute;margin-left:68.75pt;
   margin-top:0;width:119.95pt;height:119.8pt;z-index:251658240;visibility:=
visible;
   mso-wrap-style:square;mso-width-percent:0;mso-height-percent:0;
   mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:0;
   mso-wrap-distance-right:9pt;mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;
   mso-position-horizontal:right;mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;
   mso-position-vertical:absolute;mso-position-vertical-relative:text;
   mso-width-percent:0;mso-height-percent:0;mso-width-relative:page;
   mso-height-relative:page'>
   <v:imagedata src=3D"Race_Mechanoid_files/image004.png" o:title=3D""/>
   <w:wrap type=3D"square"/>
  </v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=3D160 height=3D160
  src=3D"Race_Mechanoid_files/image003.png" align=3Dright hspace=3D12 v:sha=
pes=3D"Picture_x0020_0"><![endif]>They
  are assisted by small robots called <span class=3DSpellE>Helpernoids</spa=
n>,
  who build and maintain all of the machinery for the Mechanoid civilizatio=
n.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>No one seems to know where the Mechanoids came from
  &#8211; they certainly appear to be the product of an extremely advanced,=
 but
  now vanished civilization. What happened to that parent civilization? Why=
 did
  they make the Mechanoids? Not even the <span class=3DSpellE>Zenox</span> =
or the
  <span class=3DSpellE>Quameno</span> can answer those questions.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Mechanoids are very reclusive. They describe
  themselves as guardians of the planet Utopia. This system is a forbidden =
zone
  that they fanatically defend. Their only communications are terse warning=
s to
  stay clear of their territory.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>They have no interest in expansion or growth &#8211;=
 they
  confine themselves to their planet Utopia in their home system. The
  Mechanoids appear to be very unfriendly and unwelcoming &#8211; perhaps it
  would be wise to stay clear of them.</p>
